<br>
I am currently using a weighty Polearm. And it does ok, but I still have problems with agro often.<br>
<br>
Should I look at getting my dex up (how high?) and go with 2 1hs with higher agro?<br>
<br>
What are good (cheap &lt; 500pp) agro weapons. <br>
<br>
Options I see often are<br>
Black Blade of Tormenting (tormenting)  - got one vote<br>
Short Sword of the Ykesa (ykesa)<br>
Shaded Blade (12/24, but no procs)<br>
Velium Short Blade (V shards)<br>
Glowing Black Sword (nutralize magic)<br>
K(something) k(something) (clinging darkness)<br>
Gnoll Hide Lariat?? (stun??)<br>
<br>
Thanks<br>
<br>
Also, would any 1hs dual out agro a good 2hs?<br>
<br>
And what should I look at getting my dex to before I can count on it to get agro?<br>
<br>
Thanks<br>
